snippet.title: Until Dawn: Rush of Blood - Games Preview Summer 2016 | PS VR
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/until-dawn-rush-of-blood-ps4/

From the warped minds of the team behind PS4™ horror classic Until Dawn, comes Until Dawn: Rush of Blood – a virtual reality experience to strike fear into the hearts of every trigger-happy arcade shooter fan.

May contain content inappropriate for children, visit http://www.esrb.org for rating information

PlayStation®VR is not for use by children under age 12. 
PlayStation®4 system, PlayStation®VR and PlayStation®Camera are required to experience VR functionality
